\id NEH  
\h Nehemiah 
\toc1 Nehemiah Lekhabu 
\toc2 Nehemiah 
\toc3 Nehemiah 
\mt1 NEHEMIAH  
\mt2 LEKHABU  
\mt3 Nehemiah Lekhabu Sung Thu Umdan  
\ip Thil hahsa kimaitopi khah loulai nahim, ahilouleh thil khat kimaitopi ding hahsa nasah-a ahileh hitobang ho hi Nehemiah thudol’a kon hetthemna nanei ding ahi. Nehemiah chu lamkai ahitoh kilhonin phatsih’a thil hahsa akimaitopi dan hiti hi ahi: toh thoa midang atilkhouna, thunoh baotam dinpi jouna, lhep lhahna thei hoa kon din jouna—hiti ho hi akimaitopin agalkai jouve. Chule lhagao thutoh kisaijin lamkai hina chu aneiyin, hiche gohkeu chu hilouvin; Pathen'in angensena banginhahsatna dinmun jenga jong athoh jouve, ti kicheh tah-in mudoh ahi.  
\is1 Nehemiah Lekhabu Jihpa Chule Ajih Kum  
\ip Nehemiah lekhabu hi Nehemiah ama tah in anajih ahi. Scholar ho seidan ahilouleh tahsan dan in Ezra lekhabu jong Nehemiah jih hidin atahsan’uvin, chule Nehemiah lekhabu hi 445-432 BC sunga ana kijih ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu Ajihna Lo  
\ip Nehemiah lekhabu hi Thulhun Lui sunga dia thusimbu nukhat pen ahi. Chule hiche Nehemiah lekhabu hin, Soh changa aum nauva kon, Jerusalem ahung kileu athum channa chanchin thu le ahinkhouva ahinto hou jouse chu ana jihlut ahi. Chujongleh Jerusalem kulpi bang kisah phat thudol jong ana jih lut in, Amiten atahsan uva kon’a ahung ki thahsem kitnau thudol jong ana jihlut in ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Nehemiah In Jerusalem Akhohsah  
\p
\v 1 Hacaliah chapa Nehemiah tohdoh chengse ho chu ahi, Artaxerxes in lengvai apoh kal kum somni lhin kum Kislev lhasungin, keima Nehemiah hi gamsung’a khopi lenpen Susa khopi sunga kana um'in ahi.  
\v 2 Kasopi ho lah a mikhat Hanani kitipa chun mi phabep khat toh Judah gam'a kon'in eihung vil’un ahi. Keiman amaho chu Juda te ho Babylon a asohchan nauva a konna ana kile kit ho chu itobang nauvem chule Jerusalem chu itobang nam tithu kana dongin ahi.  
\v 3 ama hon hiti hin eidonbut uve, “Sohchan naova konna hung kile Juda te chu, hinkho hahsa tah le Avella cheng namdan ten anoise lheh uve, Chule Jerusalem kulpi bang chu akisuchim nia pat, kelkot ho jouse jong meiya ana kihal lhah gam jou apat semphat louvin aum'e,” ti eiseipeh un ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche thu hi kajah phat in katou lha jengin kakap jah tai. Chuti chun nikho phabep sung chun lunghem tah in an ka-ngol’in chule van Pathen kom'a kataovin ahi.  
\v 5 “O Pakai, van Pathen,nathupeh nit ho leh nangma ngailu jingho chunga na milungset  
\p na le nakitepna chepi jinga oupe tah le tijat umtah Pathen nahi!   
\p
\v 6 Nami Israel te dinga sun le jana kataona hi venlang chule kataona hi neihin ngaipeh in! Ajeh chu keiho hi nangma douna a chonse  
\p kahi tauve, keima insung le keima tah jeng jong kachonse tauve tia ka phondoh ahi.   
\p
\v 7 Chule nalhachapa Mose a konna neipeh’u nathupeh ho le chonna dan chule neithu gah na ho kanit pouvin melse tah in kachonse tauve.  
\v 8 Chule nangman nalhachapa Mose kom'a nanaseisa, “Nangho keima kom'a nakitah lou’ule keiman chitin namtin lah a kathe cheh ding nahiuve. \x + \xo 1:8 \xt Thempu Dan 26:33\x*  
\v 9 Amavang nangho kaheng’a nahung kile hei’uva kathu peh nanit’uva hiche dungjuiya chu nachon’uva ahileh leiset kol mong geiya ana kithe chehsa hijongleu chun kamin dopsang na dinga keiman kagon pehnau gam ma chu kahin nung puilut kit diu ahi nati,” chu hingel doh kit’in. \x + \xo 1:9 \xt Danbu Ni Na 30:1-5\x*  
\v 10 Hiche nam mite hi nalhacha te ahiuve, naban gol thahat na le natha neina’a nahuhdohsa ahiuve.  
\v 11 O Pakai kataona hi lungset tah in neingai peh in! Nangma ja bolna a thanomte taona ngaipeh in, tuni hin lengpa khohsah na neimu sah inlang neilolhin sah in; lengpa lungsunga khoto na neimu sah in.” kati. Hiche phatlai chun, lengpa juhaidom in kana pange.   
\c 2  
\s1 Nehemiah Jerusalem’a Kile  
\p
\v 1 Artexerxes vaihom na kum somni lhin Nisan lhasungin, lengpa kom'a a adon ding ju kadoplut peh in ahi. Keiman akom'a khat vei cha lungkham mel kana put khahlouhel anahi.  
\v 2 Hijeh chun lengpan eina dongin, “Ipi dinga hibangtah a hi lungkham a nahim? Adammo dan la nahi pon, lungkhamna khohtah khat vang nanei hinte eiti; hichun keima kati ajalheh jengin ahi.  
\v 3 Ahinlah keiman kadonbut’in, “Lengpa hingsot’in! Keima iti kalungkham da ding ham? Kapu kapate ana kivuina khopi chu amangthah tan, chuleh akulpi kelkot ho jong meiyin akalha gamtai,” kati. \x + \xo 2:3 \xt 2 Lengte 25:8-10; 2 Thusimbu 36:19; Jeremiah 52:12-14\x*  
\v 4 Hichun lengpan eidongin’ “Aphai; chuti chu ahileh ipi lampen a kaki thopi thei ding ham?” eiti; hichun keima van Pathen kom'a kataovin;  
\v 5 Hitin kadonbut tai, “Lengpa nasohpa keima chunga khoto na naneiya nalunglhaina ahi ding leh Judah gam'a neisol’inlang kapu kapate kivuina khopi chu gasa phange” kati.  
\v 6 Hiche pet’a chu lengnu toh toukhom lhon ahin, lengpan phat itih chan naga sulut dem? itih donleh nahung kile thei dem?” eiti, Keiman phat itih chan kaga suh lut ding ham ti kahetsah jou chun aman eiphat sah peh tai.  
\v 7 Lengpa kom'a chun keiman kaseibe kitin, “Lengpa nalung alhai dinga ahile, Eupharates vadung gal lhanglam gamkaiya gam vaipo ho kom'a lekha eijih peh inlang Judah gam kajot na a agamsungu boilouhel a kajot galkai theina dingin thupeh neithot peh in,” kati.  
\v 8 “Chule lengpa thing gampo pa Asaph kom'a lekha neijih peh inlang, Hou-In kulpi khopi kulbang sah na ding leh keima chen na dingin sahna a Kamanchah ding thing eipeh theina dingin thupeh neithot peh in,” kati. Hichun Pathen'in kachunga khotona anei jal'in lengpan kathum jouse eiphal pehin ahi.  
\v 9 Eupharates vadung lhumlam gamkaiya gamvaipo ho kom kalhun phat in lengpa lekha jih ho chu kape lutin ahi. Gahseibe ding chun lengpan sakol sepai ho leh vaipo ho keima eiveng dingin eihin solpeh in ahi.  
\v 10 Ahin Horon mi Samballat leh Ammon mi Tobiah leng lhacha a pang teni hin kavai lhun ahetdoh lhon phatin Israel chate panpi ding mikhat ahungtai tin alung nom mo lheh jeng lhonin ahi.   
\s1 Nehemiah In Jerusalem Kulpi Akholchil  
\p
\v 11 Hiti hin nithum jouvin Jerusalem kaga lhung tai.  
\v 12 Jankhangin aguh in kathoudoh in mi phabep toh kahin, Pathen'in Jerusalem a eitoh sah nom ho chu koimacha ka seipeh pon ahi. Katouna sa-ngan tailou gancha dang khat cha kapui pouvin ahi.  
\v 13 Hiti chun jan khang kim in kapotdoh’un phaicham kelkot langa kacheuvin, Sial twikul chu kaho pauvin, ehbohna kelkot geiyin kacheuvin akivo chimsa pal ho leh akihal lha kakhol toh sohkeiyun ahi.  
\v 14 Chujouvin, twisam putna kelkot le lengpa twikul geiyin kacheuvin ahileh katounau sa-ngan chu songchip ho lah a chun athol tapoi.  
\v 15 Hiti chun jan khanglai chun Kidron phaicham geiyin kachen, palchu kahin kholpeh in, chujouvin kahung kilen phaicham kelkot langa kahung lut tai.  
\v 16 Hiti chun khopi vaihom hon itih a kapotdoh a ipi kaga bol ham ti ahepouve; ajeh chu keiman katoh gon chu koimacha kana hetsah pon ahi. Judah lamkai ho leh thempu ho, chule mithupi ho leh vaihom ho ahilouleh vaihom na mun'a umho khat cha kana hetsahpon ahi.  
\v 17 Tun vang keiman amaho chu kahet sah tan ahi, “Itobang hahsatna itou hitam Jerusalem hi khopigem ahitan, akelkot ho jousela maiyin akavam soh tai tihi nang hon nahe sohkei’uve; tun eihon Jerusalem kulpi pal hi sapha kitnu hitin ijum nao hi subei tao hite,” katin ahi.  
\v 18 Hiche jou chun keiman itibang Pathen kaihoi kachan ham chuleh lengpa toh iti kahung kihou lim lhon ham ti ka seipeh tan ahi.  
\v 19 Ahinlah Samballat, Tobiah le Arab mi Geshem te hon katoh gon’u chu ahet doh phat’un noise tah in eina houvun ahi. “Ipi nabol’u ham? Lengpa douna a na natoh u ham?” tin eidongun ahi.  
\v 20 Hichun keiman kadonbut’in, “Van Pathen'in eipan hu’uva eitoh chai sah diu ahi. chule keiho ama lhachaten khopi pal hi kasah phat diu ahi; amavang nang hon hiche ahin chan anei pouve, thaneina jong nanei pouve, Jerusalem khopi ahin nachan diu goujong nanei pouvin ahi,” kati.   
\c 3  
\s1 Jerusalem Kulpi Pal Akaiphat-U  
\p
\v 1 Hiche jou chun thempulen Eliashib leh thempu dang ho chun Kelngoi Kelkot chu asemphauvin ahi; hiti chun asemjou phat’un athensouvin, chuleh akot jouse jong asutoh un, Jakhat Insang kiti chan geiyin asa phauvin, achaisoh phat’un athenso’vin chuin Hananel Insung geipeh in asa phauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Jericho khopi a konna hung mipiten amaho bang chun na atongun chuban’in Imri chapa Zakkur in atongin ahi.  
\v 3 Hassenaah chapa ten Ngapi Kelkot geiyin asauvin ahi; Chule ama hon ajol jong ajam’un, akot jouse jong asuto’uvin, chule kopja le thih jol ho jong asutoh un ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche banna pal chu Hakkoz tupa Uriah chapa Meremoth in asemphan ahi. Chule ama ban’a hin Meshezabel tupa Berekiah chapa Meshullam in asempha in ahi. Chujongleh ama banin Baana chapa Zadok in asemin ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche ban in Tekoa konna hung mipite hin alamkai houvin hiche natoh na a vaihom hotoh atoh khom nomlou vangun ahung semphauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chule Khopi Kelkot luichu Paseah chapa Joiada leh Besodeiah chapa Meshullam in asempha lhonin ahi. Chule ama hon ajol ajam’un, akot ho atungdoh’un, chule kopja ho le thih jol ho jouse jong asutoh un ahi.  
\v 7 Amaho banin Gibeon a kon'in Milatiah, Meronoth a kon'in Jadon, chule Gibeon mipite Mizpah a kon a hung mipiten Eupharates lhum lam gamvaipo pa chenna mun gei asemphauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Chule hiche bana hin sanakhenga pang Harhai’ah chapa Uzziel in ana semphan ahi; chule ama ban a hin thaonamtui sema pang Hananiah in ana semphan, chule amaho hin Jerusalem kulpi pal lenpa geiyin anasem phauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Chule amaho bana pal sempha a panga chu Jerusalem gamkai akehkhat chunga lamkaiya pang Hur chapa Rephai’ah ana hi.  
\v 10 Amaho bana hin Harumaph chapa Jedai’ah kitipa hin in kotmai lam chu ana semphan; chuleh ama bana chun Hashabneiah chapa Hattush chun asemphan ahi.  
\v 11 Hiche bana hin Harim chapa Malkijah leh Pahath-moab chapa Hasshub in munchom banglai khat toh meilhum chung insang chung geiyin asempha lhonin ahi.  
\v 12 Hallohesh chapa Shallum leh achanuten abanchu asem phauvin ahi; chule ama hi Jerusalem gamkai akeh khat chunga lamkai ahiye.  
\v 13 Chule phaicham kelkot chu Hannun lamkai na in Zanoah mipiten ana semphauvin ahi, chule ama hon akot ho atung doh’un, chujongleh kopja ho le thih jol ho geiyin asutoh’un ahi. Chuleh palchu tong sangkhat le ja-nga gei Ehkul Kelkot chan geiyin ana semphauvin ahi.  
\v 14 Chule Ehkul Kelkot chu Beth-hakkerem gamkaiya lamkaiya pang Recab chapa Malkijah in asem phan; chule aman akotho atung doh in kopja ho le thih ho geiyin asutoh in ahi.  
\v 15 Mizpah gamkaiya lamkai Kol-hozeh chapa Shallum chun Twisam putna kelkot chu asemphan, chule aman achung akhun, akot ho jong atungdoh in chuleh kopja ho le thih ho geiyin asutoh in ahi. Hiche bana chun lengpa hon kom Siloam twikul pal chu asemphan chule apal chu David khopia konna kidosuh kalbi geichun asemphan ahi.  
\v 16 Hiche banna hin Bethzur gamkai akeh khat chunga lamkaiya pang Azbuk chapa Nehemiah in asemphan ahi; chule aman David insung mite lhantoh kigalsai twikul chuleh galhat ho inmun chan geiyin asemphan ahi.  
\v 17 Chule hiche banna hin Bani chapa Rehum lamkai nan Levi te phabep khat in ana semphauvin; chule hiche banna hin Keilah gamkai akeh khat chunga lamkaipa Hashabi’ah lamkai nan ana semphauvin ahi.  
\v 18 Hiche banna hin Keilah gamkai akeh khat chunga lamkaiya pang Henadad chapa Binnui lamkai nan agamsung mite nana semphauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Amaho banna Mizpah lamkai, Jeshua chapa Ezer hin pal ningkoi kom, manchah ho kikoina lang se se chu asem phan ahi.  
\v 20 Ama banna Zabbai chapa Baruch in thempulen Eliashib in kot ninga pat’in aninglang khat geiyin asemphan ahi.  
\v 21 Chule ama nunga hin Hakkoz chapa Uriah chapa Meremoth chun Eliashib in kot na kon'in aninglang khat geiyin asem phan ahi.  
\v 22 Ama banna hin thempu ho leh phaicham a cheng hon asem phauvin ahi.  
\v 23 Amaho ban ah hin Benjamin leh Hesshub amani toh kigalsai ja um chu asempha lhonin ahi; chule amani banna chun Ananiah chapoa Maasei’ah chapa Azariah chun ama inkom chu asemphan ahi.  
\v 24 Ama banna hin Henadad chapa Binnui chun Azariah inkom'a pat aningkoi gei palgol chom khat chu asemphan ahi.  
\v 25 Uzai chapa Palal chun agal langkhat in ningkoi lai chule insang laitah toh kigalsai lai, chule lengpa indan chungnung, in vengtup ho panna indan laitah chu asemphan ahi; chule ama bantah a hin Parosh chapa Pedai’ah leh;  
\v 26 Ophel vum'a cheng Hou-In lhacha a pang hotoh twi kelkot gal nisolam insang toh kimai ngat lai chu asemphauvin ahi.  
\v 27 Hiche jouchun Tekoah mipi ho ahung’uvin insang thupitah a kitung doh gal Ophel pal geiyin mun chom khat ahung semphauvin ahi.  
\v 28 Chule Sakol Kelkot chung chu thempu hon asem phauvin ahi; chule amaho khat cheh chun ama in toh kigal sai cheh chu asem phauvin ahi.  
\v 29 Abanchu Immer chapa Zadok chun ama in toh kigalsai akotmai laitah mun phabep chu asemphan, chule ama banchun solang kelkot ngahpa Shecaniah chapa Shemai’ah chun asemphan ahi.  
\v 30 Hiche banchu Shelemiah chapa Hananiah leh Zalaph chapa agup channa Hanun chun munchom lai khat asempha lhonin, alangkhat a Berekiah chapa Meshullam in ama chenna inmun gal a palchu asemphan ahi.  
\v 31 Sana kheng ho lah a mikhat Malkijah kitipa chun Hou-In lhacha ho leh kivei ho umna in chan gei kelkot ngah ho gal lang chan gei a pal chu agenphan ahi; hiche ban jongchun anunglam indan chung geiyin asembe in ahi.  
\v 32 Sana khenga pang adang ho leh kivei miho chun kelngoi kotpi ningkoiya konchun pal chu ahin semphauvin ahi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Natoh Na Doudal Te Le Nehemiah  
\p
\v 1 Keihon pal kasah phat nauva kana toh’u hi Sanballat in ahin hetdoh phat’in alunghang lheh jengin ahi; ahin ama alunghan behseh jeh in Juda te chu i-sahloutah in ahousen ahi.  
\v 2 Hiti hin aloi agolho masangle Samaria sepai lamkai ho masanga hiti hin aseiye, “Hiche Israel mimote le tah lalte hin ipi bola kingaito hiuvaham? Gan kilhaina maicham gahbol mai maiya konna hi nikhat sunga hiche pal hi agah tundoh joujeng diuva angaitou ham? Chule hiche meiyin akahsa song ho leh bohse nong nai ho hi mangcha a tohdoh ding agotnu hintem?” ati.  
\v 3 Chule akom uva um Ammon mi Tobiah chun hitin ana seiye, “Itobangin kasaphai tijonglehu, achunga khun sial khat galhai jongleh chonchim tante,” ati.  
\v 4 Hichun keima hiti hin kataove, “Vo Kapa Pathen kataonao hi neihin ngaipeh’un, keiho hi noise tah in eikihouse tauve, hijeh chun eihouset nauhi amaho chunga chuh sah inlang; chule amaho joh migam a sohchangin umsah jotan:  
\v 5 Asuhkhel nau hi nahsah mon koi hihbeh in, chule achonset naohi geldao hihbeh in, ajeh chu amaho hin natongho masang laitah a hin nangma naphin lunghang tauvin ahi,” kati.  
\v 6 Hiti hin keihon khopi pumpi kimvel chu kagen jom toupeh un hiti chun akim kalhut tauvin ahi, ajeh chu mipiten thanom tah in na atongun ahi.  
\v 7 Ahinla hitobang tah a hi natoh achal a Jerusalem pal achimsa lai jouse akisemphat hi Sanballat le Tobiah chuleh Arab mite, Amon mite le Ashdod miten ajahdoh phat’un alunghang lheh jeng tauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Hijeh chun amaho hin Jerusalem hindel khuma kisatpia suhboi dingin agong tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Ahinlah keiho Pathen hengah kataovun khopi chu kangah’un asun ajan in keiho le keiho kaki veng tauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Hichejou hin Juda mipite natongho la athachol lheh tan, song lhoh dingla atamlheh nalaiyin ahi. Hijeh chun eiho changseh in pal hi saphajou pouhite tin aphun tauvin ahi.  
\v 11 Alangkhatna kamelma teuvin jong, “Ipi thilsoh a ham ti ahetdoh kah’uvin, eihon delkhum’u hitin ithagam’uva anatohu hi isuhtang diu ahi,” tin aseiyun ahi.  
\v 12 Hitia melmate toh cheng khom Judah ho ahungun avel vel in ahung seiyun, “Muntin a konna hunguva eihung delkhum diu ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 13 Hijeh chun keiman paltom mun nemlang akilang dom mun hoa chun thalchoi angah ding kakoiyin ahi. Chule keiman ama ama insung dungjuijin chem, tengcha leh moltum kichoiya angah ding jong kaban goltoh in ahi.  
\v 14 Hiche joujin keiman thil umdan chu kavetoh in, mithupi ho leh vaihom ho chule mipi dang ho chu kakou khomin akom uvah hitin kaseiye, “Melmate jeh khun kicha hihbehun! loupitah le thaneitah Pakai chu geldoh un chuleh nasopi te, najiteu, nachateu leh na insungu huhnan galsat din pangun,” katin ahi.  
\v 15 Kamelma teu chun athilse gon’u kahehdoh’u chu ajadoh tauvin chuleh Pathen'in athilse gon’u chu asuhboipeh phat un, keiho palmun'a kana toh nao mun cheh a kakile kit tauve.  
\v 16 Ahinlah hichea konchun kamite akeh khatin bou na atongun, adangsen tengcha akidop’un, lum akichoi’un, chule thalpi akipat’un, thih sangkhol aki’ah sohkei tauve. Chuleh lamkai ho jouse chu Judah mipi ho atilkhou in apang jingun ahi.  
\v 17 Chule natong ho chun akhut langkhat in athilpoh’u chu atuh’un, chuleh akhut langkhat in manchah akichoi’un ahi.  
\v 18 Hiti chun natong ho jouse chun apang peh’uva chem akiko sohkeiyun ahi. Chule sumkon mutna pangpa chu mutdinga kigo sadem’in keikom'a aum jinge.  
\v 19 Hichun keiman mithupi ho leh vaihom ho kom leh mipi ho kom'a chun, kahet themsah in, “Inatoh’u hi akithe jal’in hijeh a chu eiho jong pal gol dungjuiya ikithe thang jengu ahi.  
\v 20 Hiche sumkon gin hi najah tengu leh agina langa chun hindel cheh jengun chutengleh I-Pathen'un gal eisat peh dingu ahi,” kati.  
\v 21 Keihon jingkah apat nilhah geiyin, chule nisoa pat nilhun geiyin na katongun ahi. Chule mi akeh khat chu manchah kichoi pumin eingah jingun ahi.  
\v 22 Keiman pal kom'a cheng ho kom'a chun Jerusalem khopi sunga hung um dau vin tin ka seipehin ahi. Hitia chu amaho le alhacha hon janleh eingah’uva pangdiu suntengleh na atohdiu ahi, kati.  
\v 23 Hiti hin hiche sunghin keiho lah a koima chan kikahin kasopiho ahin, kalhacha ho ahin, keitoh umkhom eingah ho ahin kavon’u chu sopding tilouvin kaladoh khapouve, ajeh chu phattin in manchah kakichoi jingun ahi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Vaichate Kibol Gentheina Na Kisuhtang!  
\p
\v 1 Hiche phat laitah hin pasal phabep leh ajiteuvin a Judah chanpi ho dounan kiphin na thu ahin samphong tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 ama hon hitin aseiyun ahi, “Keiho hi insung mi tamte kahiuve, hijeh chun kaki hinsona diuvin neh le chah kangaicha be uvin ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 3 Adang hon aseiyun, keihon kellhah sunga anneh kakimu na diuvin ka in ule kalouvu chuleh ka lengpileiyu katungdoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 4 Chuleh adangin aseikit’un, “Keihon kai pehna dingin kalouvu leh kalengpileiyu sumpa lah na in katung gam tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Keiho hi ahao ho insung mi mama kahiuvin, kachateu jong amaho chate tobang ahiuvin, ahinla kaki hinso theina diuva hi kachateu hi sohchang dinga suma kaki joh gam diu ahitai. Chule keihon kachanuteu hi kada kachamlou’uva kajoh gammu ahitan alonaje kahe tapouvin ahi, ajeh chu kalou’u leh ka lengpilei houhi mi kom'a katundoh gamu ahitai,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 6 Hiche alunglhai lou nau thulhuh hi kajah doh phat in kalung ahanglheh jengin ahi.  
\v 7 Giltah a lunggel kanei jouvin, mithupi ho leh vaihom ho chu kaphoh’in, “Nanghon nasopi houvin sumpa alahnauva sumthoi nalah’uhi nasuh gentheiyu ahi,” katin ahi. Hiti chun keiman hiche thu suhtohna dinga hin mipi kikhopna khat kana gongin ahi. \x + \xo 5:7 \xt Potdohbu 22:25; Thempu Dan 25:35-37; Danbu Ni Na 23:19,20\x*  
\v 8 Hiche kikhopna a hin keiman hitin kana seiye, “Eihon isopi Judah te namdang ho kom'a amaho leh amaho ana kijohdoh ho hi nung lhatdoh kitna dinga lung aki ngaito lai tah in nang hon amaho hi sohchang dingin na le joh doh kit tauvin ahi. Chule amaho hi i-jatvei lom i-lhadoh diu ham?” kati. Chujongleh ama hon akihon na diuvin ima sei ding ahepouvin ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin keiman kaseibe kitin, “Na thilbol’u hi adihpoi! I-melma nam ho hin einoise louna diuvin I-Pathen’u ginna a hi ikimanchah lou diu ham?  
\v 10 Keima tah le kasopi ho chule kana tonghon mipi ho kom'a hi sum le pai chule chang leh mim ho kana hom un ahi, ahinla tubeh hin sumthoi hi lah dau hite.  
\v 11 Nanghon alou hou le alengpilei hou, le Olive thinglei jouseu chule a in hou chu, tuni tah hin lepeh tauvin. Chule bat dinga sum, changle mim, lengpitwi le Olive thaova konna athoi nalah hou chu na le peh teitei diu ahi,” katin ahi.  
\v 12 Chule ama hon eidon but’un, “Keihon mipi ho chu lepeh sohkeijuving ting chule amahoa kon'in imacha ngeh tapou vinge, keihon nasei bang bang’a chu kabol diu ahitai,” atiuve. Hijou chun keiman thempuho le mithupi ho chule vaihom ho chu kakouvin akitepnau banga atohdoh tei na diuvin kakihahsel sah in ahi.  
\v 13 Chuphat in keiman kaponchol chu kathingin kaseitai, “Nakitepnau dungjuiya chu nabol louvu leh na insung’u leh na thilkeu houva kon'in nathing lhauhen kati,” Chule khoppi pumpin eidonbut’uvin, “Amen,” atiuvin Pakai athangvah’un ahi. Chule mipi ho chun akitepnau bang bangin atongdoh tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Nehemiah Mipite Ding’a Akiphalna  
\p
\v 14 Hiti hin kum som le ni sung in Judah gamvaipo in kapangin chule Artexerxes lengchan kal kum somni a pat kum som thumle ni chan gei, kei kahin kanoiya vaipo ho ahin katoh nau dinmun dungjuiya kachan ding dol’u chanvou chu kalapouve.  
\v 15 Gamvaipo masa hon vang mipi ho pohgih nasa tah anapoh sah un, dangka shekel som li kalval in mipi lah a neh le chah chule lengpitwi ana kidon jiuvin ahi. Chule alhachauva pangte ho jengin jong mipi chunga ana kinomsah jiuvin ahinlah keiman Pathen kagin jeh'in hiti chun kanabol pon ahi.  
\v 16 Keima tah jengin jong pal sem na a hin lunglut tah in na katongin chule gam leiset lamdoh ding jong kana gelpoi. Chule kalhacha ho jeng jong hiche pal semna ahin kana mangcha sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 17 Gam chom choma konna kholjin hungji ho tilou vin jong Judah miho vaihom ho mi ja nga le som nga hi thonlou vin an neh kakhang jingjin ahivangin keiman ima kana ngeh pon ahi.  
\v 18 Niseh a keiman neh le chah a kato doh jing chu bongchal khat, kelngoi ahilou le kelcha gup ahcha tampi ahijinge. Chule nisom seh leh donding lengpitwi suhneng jing angaiyin ahi. Ahiyeng vang'in keiman gamvaipo kahina a eikipe nehle chah kachan ding dol chu kangeh deh poi, ajeh chu mipi hon pohgih apohkhop set sau ahi.  
\v 19 Vo ka Pathen keima hiche mite dinga thil hijat kabol hi neigeldoh peh inlang hiche jeh hin phatthei neiboh in.   
\c 6  
\s1 Nehemiah Atha Got-U  
\p
\v 1 Kamelma teu Sanballat, Tobiah, Geshem kiti Arab mipale midang hon, kotpi chengse le kelkot dunga katundoh loulai vangun, Jerusalem pal chu akigen chaiyin avanglai mun khatcha aum tapoi ti amudoh phat’un;  
\v 2 Sanballat le Geshem in Ono phaicham Hakkephirim kho ah kimutou hite tin thu eihin thot in ahi. Ahinlah amani hin keima chunga thilse agon lhon ahi chu keiman kahen ahi.  
\v 3 Hijeh chun keiman adonbutna in thu hiti hin kathot in ahi, “Keiman natoh lentah khat katoh ahi, hijeh hin hungthei ponge, nangni toh kimuto ding gunsetna iti kanatoh ka ngah thei ding ham?  
\v 4 Hitobang hin amanin livei jen thu eihin thot lhonin kenjong kadonbut ngai ngaiyin kadonbut in ahi.  
\v 5 Anga-vei channan Sanballat in alhachapa kakom'ah ahin sol in akhut’ah hondohsa lekhathot khat ahinchoiye.  
\v 6 Hiche chun hitin aseiye, “Hiche vella um nam mite lah a hin thu kithang khat akijan, Geshem in jong hichu adih ahi ati, hichu ahileh nang leh Judah tehin lengpa dounan galbol ding agon ahi, hiche jeh a hi pal nasemphat’u ahi tithu kithang dungjuiya nang hi leng chang dinga kigong nahi,” akiti.  
\v 7 Aman athupoh dungjuijin nang hin Jerusalem a nangma chung chang phongdoh dingin thempu ho jong apansah e akiti, veuvin Judah gam'ah lengkhat aumtai; Hiche thu kithang hi lengpa kom'a athu hi gale lhun tei ding ahi ti nahet ding doltah ahi, hijeh chun hungin lang hiche thu hi seikhom hite.”  
\v 8 Hichun keiman thu lethuh na kapen, “Nahin thusei chu khatcha adih aumpoi, aboncha chu nangin nabol thu ngen ahi bouve,” kati.  
\v 9 Amaho hin suh kichat a chule keiho hi lunglhah sah ding chule anatoh’u hi suhtang ding atiu ahi. Hijeh chun keiman natoh chu gut tah in kamano jon ahi.  
\v 10 Khonungin, Mehetabal tupa Delaiah chapa Shemai’ah chu a in mun'a aum na a kaga chen kaga kimupi in ahi, hichun aman hitin aseiye, “Eiho Pathen Hou-In sunga kimutou hitin kot kikha khumu hite, chule namelmaten tujan na hi nahung thadiu ahi.”  
\v 11 Ahinla keiman kadonbut’in, “Koiham kei din mun'a dinga kichat jeh a jam ding ngah? Chule koiham kei dinmun'a dinga ahinkho kihuhdoh na dinga Hou-In sunga kisel ding ngah? Ahipoi hitia chu kaumlou ding ahi,” kati.  
\v 12 Pathen'in ama kom'a chun thu aseipoi ti kahei, aman hiche gaothu chu Tobiah leh Sanballat in achohdoh lhon na aseisah lhon ahi bouve ti kahet ahi.  
\v 13 ama hon kichat sah a chule chonset sah ding eigot lhon ahi bouve. Hiteng chuleh oimoa thepmo sah ding eigot lhon ahi.  
\v 14 Vo K a Pathen Tobiah leh Sanballat thilse bol ho pihi hingel doh in, chuleh keima kichatsah tei ding eigoa themgaonu Noadiah le themgao dang ho jouse jonghi hingel doh in.   
\s1 Natong Hon Natoh Achai-U  
\p
\v 15 Hiti chun ‘Elul’ lha nileh som ni le nga chan ni kasah pat niuva pat ni som nga le ni ni channin pal chu kagen chai tauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Kamel ma hou le avel a cheng mite hon ajahdoh phat’un akicha lheh jengun jum akisa lheh jengun ahi. Hiche hi Pathen panpina jal a atohdoh jouvu ahi ti ama hon ahedoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 17 Hiche ni som nga le ni ni sung hin Tobiah leh Judah mithupi ho kikah a hin lekhathot tamtah akithot to le le jengun ahi.  
\v 18 Ajeh chu Judah gam'a mi tamtah in ama kom'a hi kihahsel a kihen ohna ananeiju ahi. Ipi jeh inen itileh ama hi Arab chapa Secaniah tupa ahin, chujongleh achapa Jehohanan chun Berekiah chapa Meshullam chanu chu akipuiya akichen pi ahi.  
\v 19 Hijeh chun mihon keikom'a ama thilpha bol jeng aseiyun; kei thusei jouse jong ama henga alhut jiuvin ahi. Chule Tobiah hin keima suh kichat teina dingin lekha eihin thot jingin ahi.   
\c 7  
\p
\v 1 Pal kaget chai phat’un keiman kotpi ho chu katungdoh in chule kelkot ngah ho le lasathem ho chule Levi ho chu atoh mun che’uva kapansah in ahi.  
\v 2 Keiman Jerusalem khopi sunga vaihom dingin kasopipa Hanani kapansah in, Hananiah chu khopi kulpi vaipon kapansah in ahi; ajeh chu ama hi tahsan umtah le midang sanga Pathen jana neitah mi ahi.  
\v 3 Chule amaho kom'a chun keiman kaseiyin, “Nikhat sungin ni ahasat laisen kelkot chu honsan koi hih un, chuleh kelkot ngah ho chun kot anga lai sung seuvin khah’unlang kotchu kamchah un. Chule Jerusalem'a cheng ho chu kot ngah dingin pan mun peuvin, chule phattin in nga sah jouvin, chule loikhat chu apan mun’uva umden’u hen lang loikhat chu ama cheh inmaiya ngasah un,” katin ahi.   
\s1 Nehemiah In Sohchang’a Hung Kile Kit Ho Min Asut Lut  
\p
\v 4 Hiche pet chun khopi chu alen in akijal in ahi, ahinla asunga cheng mite chu alhomin ahi. Chule achen nau in ho jong chu sahphat lou ahi.  
\v 5 Hiti chun Pathen'in eihetsah dungjuijin, khopi sunga lamkai ho leh mithupi ho chu khosunga cheng milhom ho chutoh kakou khomun aminu kajih lut sah in ahi. Chule keiman Judah gam'a ana kile masaho min kijihlut na lekhabu chu kana mudoh in ahi, hichea kamu chu hiche ho hi ahi:  
\v 6 Hiche Judah te asohchan nauva hungkile doh a gamchom choma ana kithe-thang ho chu ahiuve. Chule leng Nebuchednezzer in Babylona ana puilut ana chenna ngaisau Jerusalem le Judah khopi chom choma tua lelut kit ho chu ahiuve.  
\v 7 Alamkai houchu, Zerubbabel, Jeshua, Nehemiah, Seraiah, Reelaiah, Nahamani, Mordecai, Bilshan, Mispar, Bigvai, Rehum, chuleh Baanah ahiuve. Hiche Israel chate akithe thang nauva konna hung kile kit ho chu ahiuve:  
\v 8 Parosh insung mite mihem sangni le ja khat le som sagi le ni ahiuve.  
\v 9 Shephatiah insung mite chu mihem jathum le som sagi le ni ahiuve.  
\v 10 Arah insung mite chu mihem jagup le som nga le ni ahiuve.  
\v 11 Pahath Moab insung mite chu mihem(Jeshua le Joab chilhah ho) sangni le ja get le som le get ahiuve.  
\v 12 Elam insung mite chu mihem sang khat le jani toh som nga le li ahiuve.  
\v 13 Zattu insung mite chu mihem ja get le som li le nga ahiuve.  
\v 14 Zaccai insung mite chu mihem ja sagi le somgup ahiuve.  
\v 15 Binnui insung mite chu mihem jagup le som li le get ahiuve.  
\v 16 Bebai insung mite chu mihem jagup le somni le get ahiuve.  
\v 17 Azgad insung mite chu mihem sangni le jathum le somni le ni ahiuve.  
\v 18 Adonikam insung mite chu mihem jagup le somgup le sagi ahiuve.  
\v 19 Bigvai insung mite chu mihem sangni le som gup le sagi ahiuve.  
\v 20 Adin insung mite chu mihem jagup le som nga le nga ahiuve.  
\v 21 Ater insung mite chu (Hezekiah chilhah) mihem somko le get ahiuve.  
\v 22 Hashum insung mite chu mihem jathum le somni le get ahiuve.  
\v 23 Bezai insung mite chu mihem jathum le som ni le li ahiuve.  
\v 24 Jorah insung mite chu mihem jakhat le som le ni ahiuve.  
\v 25 Gibbar insung mite chu mihem somko le nga ahiuve.  
\v 26 Bethlehem le Netophah mipite chu jakhat le somget le get ahiuve.  
\v 27 Anathoth mipite chu mi jakhat le somni le get ahiuve.  
\v 28 Beth-azmaveth mipite chu mi somli le ni ahiuve.  
\v 29 Kiriath-jearim, Kephirah le Beeroth mipite chu mihem ja sagi le somli le thum ahiuve.  
\v 30 Ramah le Geba mipite chu mihem jagup le somni le khat ahiuve.  
\v 31 Michmash mipite chu mihem ja khat le somni le ni ahiuve.  
\v 32 Bethel le Ai mipite chu mihem ja khat le somni le thum ahiuve.  
\v 33 Lhumlam Nebo mipite chu mi somnga le ni ahiuve.  
\v 34 Lhumlam Elam khomite chu mi sang khat le jani le somnga le li alhinguve.  
\v 35 Harim khomite chu mi jathum le somni ahiuve.  
\v 36 Jericho khomite chu mi jathum le somli le nga ahiuve.  
\v 37 Lod, Hadid le Ono khomite chu mihem ja sagi le somni le khat ahiuve.  
\v 38 Senaah khomite chu mihem sang thumle jako le som thum ahiuve.  
\v 39 Hiche ho hi thempuho ava cheh nauva konna hung kile kit ahiuve: Jedaiah insung mite (Jeshua chilhah te ahiuve) amaho chu mihem jako le som sagi le thum ahiuve.  
\v 40 Immer insung mite chu mihem sang khat le som nga le ni ahiuve.  
\v 41 Pashhur insung mite chu mi sang khat le jani le somli le sagi ahiuve.  
\v 42 Harim insung mite chu mi sangkhat le som le sagi ahiuve.  
\v 43 Hiche ho hi ava cheh nauva konna hung kinungle Levi te chu ahiuve: Jeshua le Kadmiel insung mite (Hodaviah chilhah te ahiuve) chu mihem som sagi le li ahiuve.  
\v 44 Asaph insung mite lathem ho chu ahiuve amaho chu mi jakhat le somli le get ahiuve.  
\v 45 Chule kelkot ngah a pang Shallum, Ater, Talmon Akkub, Hatita le Shobai insung mite chu mihem jakhat le somthum le get ahiuve.  
\v 46 Ava cheh nauva konna hung kile doh kit Hou-In lhacha ho Ziha, Hasupha, Tabbaoth chilhah ho chu:  
\v 47 Keros, Siaha, Padon;  
\v 48 Lebanah, Hagabah, Shalmai;  
\v 49 Hanan, Giddel, Gahar;  
\v 50 Reaiah, Rezin, Nekoda;  
\v 51 Gazzam, Uzza, Paseah;  
\v 52 Besai, Meunim, Nephushesim;  
\v 53 Bakbuk, Hakupha, Harhur;  
\v 54 Bazlith, Mehida, Harsha;  
\v 55 Barkos, Sisera, Temah;  
\v 56 Neziah leh Hatipha;  
\v 57 Leng Solomon lhacha a pangho ava cheh nauva konna hung kile doh ho chu; Sotai, Hassophereth, Peruda chilhah ho ahiuve.  
\v 58 Talaph, Dakkon, Giddel;  
\v 59 Shephatiah, Hattil, Pokereth, Hazzebaim le Ami ahi.  
\v 60 Hou-In lhacha ho leh Solomon lhacha ho chilhah ho abonchauvin mihem jathum le somko le ni ahiuve.  
\v 61 Loichom ho: Telmelah, Telharsha, Cherub, Addon le Immer khopi hoa konna hung kile doh ho ahiuve. Ahinla ama hon a insung chu Israel chilhah akon ahi nao photchenna apethei pouvin ahi.  
\v 62 Hiche loi ho hin Delaiah, Tobiah, le Nekoda insung miho ahopin ahi, chule amaho chu abonun mihem jagup le som li le ni ahiuve.  
\v 63 Thempuho insung mite Hobaiah, Hakkoz, chule Bar-zillai jong ahung kileuve (hiche Bar-zillai kitipa hin Gilead na konna Bar-zillai chilhah numei khat akichen pin ama hin hichenu insung mite min alah ahi).  
\v 64 Amaho hin phung kisutna a aminu ahin hol’uvin amudoh pouvin ahi, hijeh chun amaho hi thempu kin chu akitoh sah tapouvin ahi.  
\v 65 Chule gamvaipo pan thempuhon Urim le vangvet na Thummim mangcha a Pakai adoh tokah-uva kilhaina a kitohdohsa ho chu thempu hina a anehlou diuvin aseipeh in ahi. \x + \xo 7:65 \xt Potdohbu 28:30; Danbu Ni Na 33:8\x*  
\v 66 Chule Judah mi ahung kinungle ho chu abonun mihem sang somli le sangni toh jathum le som gup alhinguvin ahi.  
\v 67 Mihem hijat jou jong chun asohteu pasal le numei ho chu mihem sang sagi le jathum le somthum le sagi ahiuve; chule lasa a pangho chu numei le pasal abonchauvin mihem ja ni le som le nga ahiuve.  
\v 68 Asakol chengseu chu jasagi le somthum le gup ahin chule sakol pol chengse jong chu jani le somli le nga ahi.  
\v 69 Chujongleh asa ngongsang chengseu chu jali le som thumle nga ahin, sangan chengse chu sang gup le jasagi le somni alhinge.  
\v 70 Chule aphung sung uva insung upa cheh mi phabep in jong Sana daric sangkhat le kisilna kong som nga toh thempu von ja-nga le som thum jen Hou-In sah na dingin thil kholna a chun atoh doh jengun ahi.  
\v 71 Chujongleh apu apauva phung upa loikhat injong natohna a manchah dingin sana daric sang som ni le dangka sang ni le ja sagi le som nga atohdoh un ahi.  
\v 72 Chule mipi adang dangin atokhom’u chu sana sang som ni le dangka sangni le ja nga toh thempuho von ding somgup le sagi atoh doh un ahi.  
\v 73 Hitobang tah hin thempuho, Levi te, chule kotngah ho, lasaho, Hou-In lhacha ho, chule milham ho phabep Jerusalem kom'ah achengun ahi. Chule mipi adang ho chengse chu Israel gamsung amaho khopi cheh’uva ale chenlut tauvin ahi. Lha sagi lhinin vang Israel te akhosung cheh uva achenglut soh tauve. \x + \xo 7:73 \xt 1 Thusimbu 9:2; Nehemiah 11:3\x*   
\c 8  
\s1 Ezra’n Mipi Danthu Asimpeh  
\p
\v 1 Mipiho chu abonchauvin twiphung kelkotna chun lung gel khat neiyin ahung kikhom un ahi. Hichun ama hon Ezra kom'a Pathen'in Israel te nit dinga anapeh Mose dan lekhabu chu ahin pohdoh dingin a ngeh tauve.  
\v 2 Hiti chun Lha sagi chule niget lhinnin Ezra thempu pan jong hiche danthu lekhabua hi numei le pasal chuleh chapang thu hethei jouse dingin ahin podoh tan ahi.  
\v 3 Aman twiphung kelkot phung sung aningkoi laiya chun jingkah apat sunkim geiyin mipi ho jouse hetthei dingin ahin simdoh in ahi. Chule mijousen dan lekhabua asimdoh ho chu angai sohkeiyuvin ahi.  
\v 4 Ezra chu hiche ding monga kisem thingpeh kidosang mun'a chun adingin ahi. Ama jetlam'a chun Mattithiah, Shema, Anaiah, Uriah, Hilkiah chule Maasseiah ana dingun ahi. Chule aveilama chun Pedaiah, Meshael, Malkijah, Hashum, Hashbaddanah, Zechariah, chule Meshullam ana dingun ahi.  
\v 5 Ezra chu mipi hon amusohkeina diuvin mun sanglai’ah ana dingin ahi.  
\v 6 Hiti chun Ezra in Pakai Pathen thupitah chu thangvah na anapen ahileh mipi ho chun akhut’u ana domsang un, “Amen! Amen!” anatiuvin ahi. Hijeh chun tollah abohkhup mun Pakai chibai aboh’un ahi.  
\v 7 Mipiho chu adin mun cheh a adingun, Levi te lah a kon'in Jeshua, Bani, Sherebiah, Jamin, Akkub, Shabbethai, Hodiah, Maaseiah, Kelita, Azariah, Jozabad, Hanan chule Pelaiah chun danthu chu mipi ho ahillun ahi.  
\v 8 ama hon Pathen danbua kon'in asimdoh’un, abih bih in mipi ho hetthei tah dingin hilchet na aneiyun ahi.  
\v 9 Hichejou chun gamvaipo Nehemiah, Ezra thempupa le danthu thempa chule mipi hilla pang Levi te chutoh akikhom uvin mipi ho jah a chun aseiyun, “Tuni hi na Pakai Pathen’u maiya nikho theng ahi, lunghem hih’un kap jong kap hih’un,” atiuve. Ajeh chu dan thucheng ho chu ajah phat’uva mipi chu kapgam jeng uva ahitai.  
\v 10 Chuleh Nehemiah chun aseiben, “Cheuvin lang an twitah tah ganeuvin lang donthei atwitah tah gadon un kipa thanop gabol un. Anei joulou ho jong chu nachan’u gachan khompi uvin, ajeh chu tuni hi Pakaiya nikho theng ahi, lungthoina nei hih’un, lung kham na jong nei hih’un, ajeh chu Pakaiya nakipa nau hi nathahat nao ahi,” ati.  
\v 11 Levi ten jong mipite chu alhamon’un, “Thipbeh in um’un, kap hih un ajeh chu tuni hi nikho theng ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 12 Hiti chun mipite chu golvah an neding leh don dingin anei joulou ho pan hu ding leh kipah tah a ankong um dingin apotdoh tauve, ajeh chu ama hon Pathen thucheng aja tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Lhambuh Kut Aman-U  
\p
\v 13 Ajing nikho nin mipi ho lah a insung lamkai ho leh thempu ho, Levi ho acheovin danthu them Ezra chu danthu hilchetbe dingin aga tem’un ahi.  
\v 14 Dan chu akholchilbe phat’un Pathen'in Mose mangcha a athupeh dungjuiya hiche lhasunga kut kibol sunga chu Israel lhambuh sunga umdiu ahi ti amudoh un ahi. \x + \xo 8:14 \xt Thempu Dan 23:33-36,39-43; Danbu Ni Na 16:13-15\x*  
\v 15 Hiche hi ama hon aphondoh uva akhodung jouseu leh Jerusalem khopi sunga aphondoh diu ahin, “Potdoh’uvin lang mol le lhang tinna cheuvin, Olive thingbah ho hijongleh, theimi vom doho hihen lang, tumthing do ho hijongleh thingna do adang dang hijongleh hiche Lhambuh Kut bolna dingin hinpolut lut’uvin tia kisun ahi,” tia aphondoh diu amudoh tauve.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun mipi chu apotdoh’uvin akisei chengse chu ahinpolut sohkeiyuvin, abonchauvin Lhambuh Kut chu abolcheh’uvin, ain chung cheh leh alhonglai dung cheh’u chule Pathen Hou-In lhong dunga chun abol uvin, twiphung inning kelkot phunga jong, Ephraim kelkot phunga jong abol abol sohkei juve.  
\v 17 Hitobang tah hin sohchan na a konna hung kile kit miho chun Lhambuh Kut abol’uvin, chule lhambuh jenga achenguve, ijeh-inem itileh Nun chapa nikholaiya pat hiche nikho geiyahi Israel chaten hitobanga hi anabol khah lou laiyu ahi. Hiche ahi kipa thanopna lentah ana um doh in ahiye.  
\v 18 Hiche kut nisagi sunghin niseh le Ezra in Pathen danthubua kon'in asimdoh jingin ahi. Chujouvin aniget chan ni in danthu dungjuijin khoppi thupitah ana bolun ahi.   
\c 9  
\s1 Mipin Achonset Nao Aphon-U  
\p
\v 1 Chuche lha nisomni le ni li nin, mipi akikhom kit’un, tuchung hin an angol’un khaodip pon asil’un, aluchunguva vut akinu’uvin ahi.  
\v 2 Israel chilhah ho jouse gamchom miho a kon'in akidal se uvin chule amaho chonset na le apu apateu chonsetna aphongdoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Pakai Pathen danbu a konna akisim phong tengleh, nidan thum sungin adinnau mun'ah ading chahkheh jiuvin ahi. Chujou tengleh nidan thum ma achonset nau phondoh na le Pakai a Pathen’u chibai bohnan amangun ahi.  
\v 4 Levi te - Jeshua, Bani, Kadmiel, Shebaniah, Bunni, Sherebiah, Bani, chuleh Kenani- hichenghi Levi te kalbia adingun Pakai a Pathen u kom’ah othong sangtah in asamun apentho jengun ahi.  
\v 5 Chujou chun Levi te lamkaiho chu: Joshua, Kadmiel, Bani, Hashabneiah, Sherebiah, Hodiah, Shebaniah, chule Pethahiah chun mipi ho chu ahin sam in, hiti hin ajah uvah ahinsei taove: “Dingdoh uvin lang Pakai na Pathen’u thangvah un, ajeh chu ama tonsot tonsotna hingjing jeng ahi,” atiuve. Hijouchun amaho ataovun, “Namin loupi hi vahchoiyin umhen! Phatthei bohna le thangvahna ho jouse chunga choisangin umhen!” atiuve.  
\v 6 “Nangma changseh bou Pakai nahi. Nangin vanho leh vanthamjol chuleh ahsi jouse nasem ahi. Nangin leiset le twikhanglen chuleh asunga umho jouse nasem ahi. Nangin aboncha hi nahoibit ahin vanna vantil te jousen chibai naboh un ahi.”  
\v 7 “Nangma hi Pakai Pathen nahin Ur gam'a um Chaldea mite lah a konna Abram nana lhendoh a nahin puidoh a, amin jong Abraham a nakhel peh ahi.” \x + \xo 9:7 \xt Semtilbu 11:31; 12:1; \xt Semtilbu 17:5\x*  
\v 8 “Aman kitah na ana subulhit jeh'in Canaan mite, Hit mite, Amon mite, Periz mite, Jebus mite, chule Gargash mite, gamhi ama leh achilhah te peh dingin kitepna nana neipi in ahi. Chuleh nangin nakitepna bangin nana tongdoh in ahi. Ajeh chu nangma hi aseidohsa thuchenga kitah jing jenga nahi.” \x + \xo 9:8 \xt Semtilbu 15:18-21\x*  
\v 9 “Nangin kapu kapateu Egypt gam'a aum laiyuva agenthei nau nana mupeh in, chuleh twikhanglen panga akanao nangaipeh in ahi.” \x + \xo 9:9 \xt Potdohbu 3:7; \xt Potdohbu 14:10-12\x*  
\v 10 “Hiti chun kapu kapateu anabol genthei jeh’un nangman Pharaoh leh avaihomho chuleh amipite dounan melchihna thilkidangtah tah nana boldoh in ahi.” \x + \xo 9:10 \xt Potdohbu 7:8—12:32\x*  
\v 11 “Nangman twikhanglen chu nana homkhen in namite tolgo’a lam nana jotsah in ahi. Chule nangman agalmiteu chu twikhanglen sunga nana lehlut’in ahi. Chujongleh amaho chu twipi noilanga song bangin analhum mang jengun ahi.” \x + \xo 9:11 \xt Potdohbu 14:21-29; \xt Potdohbu 15:4,5\x*  
\v 12 “Nangman kapu kapateu chu sun tengleh meilom in nana puiyin, jan tengleh meikong lomin nana puiyin, alampi diu nana musah jingin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:12 \xt Potdohbu 13:21,22\x*  
\v 13 “Chule nangma Sinai molsang chunga nahung kumlhan chuleh vanna kon'in nahin seiyin ahi, che na daan le thuhil dihtah tah nanapen chuleh thupeh leh thugahna hoitah tah nana pen ahi.” \x + \xo 9:13 \xt Potdohbu 19:18—23:33\x*  
\v 14 “Chule nangman nachol ngah nitheng chung chang hilchet na jong nana pen chule nangman nalhachapa Mose mangchan nathupeh ho le nathu gah na chuleh nathuhil ho anit diuvin nana seipeh in ahi.”  
\v 15 “Chuti chun amaho agil’u akel tengleh van'a kon'in changlhah nana pen; adangchah tengule songpia kon'in twi napen ahi; Nangin peh dinga nana tep peh gamho alokhum diuvin thupeh jong nana pen ahi.” \x + \xo 9:15 \xt Potdohbu 16:4-15; \xt Potdohbu 17:1-7; \xt Danbu Ni Na 1:21\x*  
\v 16 “Ahinlah kapu kapateu chu ana kiletsah’un chuleh ana louchal’un ahi, chuleh nathupeh chu ana nahsah pouvin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:16 \xt Minbu 14:1-4; Danbu Ni Na 1:26-33\x*  
\v 17 “Amaho nathua nun ding ana nom pouvin, chuleh amaho dinga thilkidang nana bolpeh ho ana geldoh jitapouvin ahi. Chusangin alouchal’un Egypt’a asoh channa languva le puikit dingin lamkai ana kilhen doh’un ahi! Ahiyeng vang'in nangma hi mi ngaidam hat, milungset them le mikhoto them, lunghang vah lou chuleh ngailutna dimset Pathen nahi.” \x + \xo 9:17 \xt Potdohbu 34:6; Minbu 14:18\x*  
\v 18 “ama hon bongnou tobang milimsemthu ana kisem doh’uva chuleh hitia ana seiyuva, hiche hi na Pathen’u Egypt a konna nahin puidoh pao chu ahi anatiuvin, hitobang tah hin Pathen taitom na chu ana neitaovin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:18 \xt Potdohbu 32:1-4\x*  
\v 19 “Ahiyeng vang'in na mikhoto na alet jeh in nangin gamthip gam'a chun nana dalha pon ahi. Suntengleh meilom in napuiyin, jantengleh mei kongin napui jing nalaiyin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:19 \xt Danbu Ni Na 8:2-4\x*  
\v 20 “Naphat na Lhagao chu mangchan nana hiljing nalaiyin, agilkel tengule aneh diuvin vanna kon'in Manna napen adangchah tengule adon diu twi nape jingin ahi.  
\v 21 “Kum somli sungin gamthip noiya nana khoukhah in, chuleh imacha lhahsam na anatoh khapouvin ahi. Aponsil’u jong asepon chuleh akengu jong ana napon ahi.”  
\v 22 “Chutengleh nangin kapu kapateu chu lenggam ho leh namdang ho chunga galjona nanapen chuleh namite hi gamsung ningkoi jousea nana koiyin ahi. Ama hon Heshbon lengpa Sihon toh Bashan lengpa Og gam jong anala uvin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:22 \xt Minbu 21:21-35\x*  
\v 23 “Nangman achilhah teu chu ahsi jat naphah sahin apu apateu nana teppeh agama chun napui lutin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:23 \xt Semtilbu 15:5; 22:17; \xt Joshua 3:14-17\x*  
\v 24 “Amaho analut’un agamu analahpeh’un ahi; chule nangman nam pumpi amasanguva nana sunem in ahi. Chule gamsunga ana cheng Canaan mite jeng jong thaneilou bangin nana lhan ahi! Hiti chun namiten hiche nam ho hi aleng teu pumin anop nop ana lotauvin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:24 \xt Joshua 11:23\x*  
\v 25 “Kapu kapateuvin, kulpi kigen khum akhopi ho ahin, agam phalai jouseu ahin, analahpeh’un ahi. Chule thil le lo phatah tah dimset in ho jong atou phauvin, twikul kigeihomsa ho leh lengpilei chuleh OIive thinglei le theiphung tamtah alahpeh’un ahi. Hiti chun ama hon lung nachim set’in athaodoh tokah seuvin aneuvin naphatthei bohna lhingset’a ana kivah’un ahi.” \x + \xo 9:25 \xt Danbu Ni Na 6:10,11\x*  
\v 26 “Ahiyeng vang'in amaho ana louchal’un, chuleh nangma dounan ana kiphin nalaiyuvin ahi; chule nadanthu ana nungsun’un, nathemgao ten na-henga hung kile dinga ana gihsal jeh un ana that gam’un, chule nangma dounan thet um tahtah thil anabol tauvin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:26 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 2:11-16\x*  
\v 27 “Hijeh chun nangman agalmiteu kom'a nana pedohjin, ama hon ana sugenthei jiuvin ahi. Ahivangin ama hon athoh gimuva nakom'a ahung tao tengule nangman vanna kon'in ataonao nangai peh kit jin; chule nami khoto na jal’in nangin ahuhdoh diu nasolpeh kityin, ama hon agal miuva kon'in aga huhdoh juivin ahi.”  
\v 28 “Ahinlah ama hon olna ahin muphat phat’ule avelin nangma mitmun thilse ahin bol kit jiuvin; chuleh nangin agal mihou noiyah nasunem kit jin ahi. Ahiyeng vang'in ama hon kap pum puma panpi ngaicha a nangma kom ahinbel tengule van'a kon'in ataonao nahin sanpeh kitjin ahi. Chuti chun nami khoto na kidangtah jal'in nangin avel vel in nahuhdoh kit jin ahi.”  
\v 29 “Nangman na danthua ahung kilehei kitna diuvin nagih saljin ahinla amaho akiletsah un, alouchal’un, nathupeh anah sahmo jiuvin ahi. Chule na danthu ho hi ajuiju leh ahindoh jeng theina diu jong ajui nom pouvin ahi; amaho alouchal’un nangma nanung ngat’un nathu angai nom pouvin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:29 \xt Thempu Dan 18:5\x*  
\v 30 “Na mingailutna jal’in kum hijat pi hi nahin khongaiyin ahi; chule nangman na Lhagao Theng nahin sol in, aman themgao ho mangchan agihsal sahjin ahi. Ahinla ama hon anahsah deh jipouve! Hijeh chun nangman agamsung miho khutna gal na lel sahjin ahi.” \x + \xo 9:30 \xt 2 Lengte 17:13-18; 2 Thusimbu 36:15,16\x*  
\v 31 Ahinlah na mikhoto na anat sat jeh in amaho chu nasu mangpai deh pon chule nadonda deh pon ahi. Itobanga lungset them leh khoto them nahi hitam?”  
\v 32 “Tun vang ka Pathen’u loupi tah leh thahat tah chuleh gimneitah ami ngailutna longlou puma akitepna nit jing Pathen, kathoh gimnao hi nahsah mon neikoi peh hihbeh’un; ajeh chu Assyria lengten eichotpha uva pat tuni geihin keiho le ka lengteu, kalamkai teu, ka themputeu, le kapu kapateu, namite ho jouse chunga hin hahsatna nasatah achutan ahi.” \x + \xo 9:32 \xt 2 Lengte 15:19,29; 17:3-6; Ezra 4:2,10\x*  
\v 33 “Nei-engbol chan’un nangma hi nadih jinge, chule keiho kachonset val jeh uvin nangman kachan diuva kilom bep neipeh jiu ahi.”  
\v 34 “Kaleng teu, ka lamkaiteu, ka themputeu, kapu kapate uvin na daan anit pouvin, na daan thupeh leh nagihsal na jong anahsah pouvin ahi.”  
\v 35 “ama hon lenggam tum aneiyun, nangman naphat naho nabuhlhah khum vangun ama hon nangma najen pouve; chule nangman gampha tah leh gam lentah napen ahinlah ama hon athilse bolnauva kon'in ahung kilehei nom deh pouve.”  
\v 36 “Hijeh chun tuni kho hin, nangin kapu kapa teuvin nengtah le lungmong tah a anehdiu gampha tah napeh na mun'a hin sohchangin kaum tauve! Hiche gampha lai tah a hin kasoh changtauve.”  
\v 37 “Kachonset jeh’uvin hiche gamsung sohdoh ga phatah tah ho hi nangin keiho chunga vaihom dinga na tun lengho khut nah achugam tan ahi; chule ama hon keiho chungleh kagancha hou chunga tha aneitauve. Chujongleh ama hon adei deiyin eimangchauvin keiho kagenthei lheh jengtauve,” atiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Mipi Athu Ngai Dia Anop-U  
\p
\v 38 Hichun mipi hon adonbut’un, “Hiche chung changa hin keihon kitepna giltah kaneiyun, hichu kajih lut’un ahi. Hiche mohor kinam khum thulhuhna lekha chunga hin ka lamkaiteu, Levi te, chuleh kathempuhou min achongin ahi,” atiuvin ahi.   
\c 10  
\p
\v 1 Hiche thulhuhna lekha hi suhdih na le suhdet na akineiyin, chuleh anoiya min chong ho hin kikhut hen na aneiyun ahi: Gamvaipopa, Hacaliah chapa Nehemiah chule Zedekiah ahiuve.  
\v 2 Noiya thempu ho cheng: Seraiah, Azariah, Jeremiah;  
\v 3 Pashhur, Amariah, Malkijah;  
\v 4 Hattush, Shebaniah, Malluch;  
\v 5 Harim, Meremoth, Obadiah;  
\v 6 Daniel, Ginnethon, Baruch;  
\v 7 Meshullam, Abijah, Mijamin;  
\v 8 Maaziah, Bilgai, leh Shemaiah, hicheng hi thempu ho ahiuve.  
\v 9 Noiya ho hi Leviho ahiuve: Azaniah chapa Jeshua, Henadad insunga kon Binnui, Kadmiel;  
\v 10 Chuleh aloi agol Levi ho: Shebaniah, Hodiah, Kelita, Pelaiah, Hanan;  
\v 11 Mica, Rehob, Hashabiah;  
\v 12 Zaccur, Sherebiah, Shebaniah;  
\v 13 Hodiah, Bani, Beninu;  
\v 14 Noiya ho hi lamkai ho ahiuve: Parosh, Pahath-Moab, Elam, Zattu, Bani;  
\v 15 Bunni, Azgad, Bebai;  
\v 16 Adonijah, Bigvai, Adin;  
\v 17 Ater, Hezekiah, Azzur;  
\v 18 Hodiah, Hashum, Bezai;  
\v 19 Hariph, Anathoth, Nebai;  
\v 20 Magpiash, Meshulam, Hezir;  
\v 21 Meshezebel, Zadok, Jaddua;  
\v 22 Pelatiah, Hanan, Ananiah;  
\v 23 Hosea, Hananiah, Hasshub;  
\v 24 Hallohesh, Pilha, Shobek;  
\v 25 Rehum, Hashabnah, Maaseiah;  
\v 26 Ahiah, Hanan, Anan;  
\v 27 Malluch, Harim, chule Baanah, ahiuve.   
\s1 Mipi Kitepna  
\p
\v 28 Chubanna mipi adang ho, thempu ho, Levi te, kotngah a pangho, lasa a pang ho, chule Hou-In lhacha a pang ho chuleh Pathen danthu nitdinga agamsunga midang Hou-In neilou ho a konna hung kichom se doh ho aji le achateu le achanu teu toh chule thu hechen theiya kikhan lhit ho chengsechun;  
\v 29 Alamkaiteu nung ajui jun ahi, jeh chu Pathen'in Mose mangcha a ahinpeh Pathen daan chu jui dingin akihahsel’un, chule asuhkeh’uva ahileh gaosap na chang dingin akitepmun ahi. I-Pakaiyu thupeh ho chonna ho le kigah na ho chu phate keicha jui dingin giltah in kitepna aneiyun ahi.  
\v 30 “Hiti hin keihon agamsung mi hounei lou ho dinga kachanu teu kapeh loudiu chujongleh kachapa teu vin jong amaho chanute jong akichenpi loudiuvin kitepna kaneiyuve.” \x + \xo 10:30 \xt Potdohbu 34:16; Danbu Ni Na 7:3\x*  
\v 31 “Chule keihon agamsunga chengte cholngah ni ahilou le nikhotheng dang nia kiveina thil ho ahilouleh changle mim ho ahung joh’u jong choh peh lou dingin kaki tep’un ahi. Chujongleh kum sagi alhin seh le kagamsungu kaki choldo sah diu, chule eibat hou jouse ka ngaidam dingu ahi.” \x + \xo 10:31 \xt Potdohbu 23:10,11; Thempu Dan 25:1-7; \xt Danbu Ni Na 15:1,2\x*  
\v 32 “Chutengleh ka Pathen’u Hou-In kin bol na a mandin kumseh a shekel khat hop thum'a hop khat kapeh jingna diuvin keiho le keiho kacham chamun kakigah jing uvin ahi.” \x + \xo 10:32 \xt Potdohbu 30:11-16\x*  
\v 33 “Vetsahnan changlhah toding ahin, tantih nei louva lhosoh thilto ding ahin, cholngah nikho nitding hihen lang, lhathah nikho kut bolding hijongleh aphat tepsa kut ho nit ding jong, chule thil theng todoh ding jong, Israel chate kithoina dinga chonset jeh a thilto ding ho jong, chujongleh ka Pathen’u Hou-In natohna dinga manchah ding jouse kapeh diuvin kakitem tauve.”  
\v 34 “Hitobang chun ti ding thing toh'a pang dingin jong keihon thempu ho pang ding hihen lang, Levi te pang ding hileh, mipi pang dinga lom hijongleh phun kisan’uvin, chule athing tithei chu ka Pathen’u Hou-In sunga poh lutna, kapu kapateu insung kailhah dola kitol a kum simseh leh aphat kitep phat phatna poh lut ding dan thu lekhabua kisun banga Pakai ka Pathen’u maicham chunga ti dingin kagouvin ahi.”  
\v 35 “Chujongleh keiho le keiho kacham cham’uvin kigahna kaki bol’uvin, kaleiset lhosohu amasa pen le thing gathei namkim aboncha agamasa chengse hi kumseh le Pakai Hou-In a todoh masah jing ding katiu ahi.” \x + \xo 10:35 \xt Potdohbu 23:19; 34:26; Danbu Ni Na 26:2\x*  
\v 36 “Chujongleh k a Pathen’u insunga lha a pang thempupa henga chun kachateu apeng masa hihen lang, kagancha apeng masa ho lah hijongleh danthu lekhabua kisun banga chu kabongu peng masa jouse leh kakelngoiyu apeng masa kahin pui cheh dingu katiu ahitai.” \x + \xo 10:36 \xt Potdohbu 13:2\x*  
\v 37 “Chutengleh thempu ho hengle k a Pathen’u indan sung dunga chu kaneh diu an kithuh masapen leh kathil todiu jong, thing gathei jouse ga jong lengpitwi le thaotwi jong hinchoi lut ding katiu ahi; hitobang ahi kalho gao kalousohu Levi te henga hopsom hinchoi peh ding katiu ahi, ajeh chu kakho dung jouseuva hopsom donga pangji chu Levi te bou ahiuve.” \x + \xo 10:37 \xt Minbu 18:21\x*  
\v 38 “Hichea hi Aaron chapa thempupa chu Levi ten hopsom akisan ding tengu leh akom uva um jing ding amaho toh kilhon ding ahi; chule Levi miho chun hopsom jousea konna hopsom kibolson chu k a Pathen’u Hou-In sung, insung dansunga thil kholna mun dunga ahinpoh lutdiu ahiye.” \x + \xo 10:38 \xt Minbu 18:26\x*  
\v 39 “Ijeh-inem itileh Israel chate leh Levi chaten chang kidong doh ho leh lengpitwi kidong doh ho thaotwi kidong doh ho chu ahin pohuva Hou-In dansung dung, munthenga manchah ding khon ho kikoina mun kinbol la pang thempu ho hengleh kelkot ngah a pangho heng, lasa ho henga ahinpoh lutdiu ahi. Chule keihon k a Pathen’u Hou-In chu donlouva kakoi kit louhel diu ahi.”   
\c 11  
\s1 Mipin Jerusalem Alo-U  
\p
\v 1 Mipi lamkai ho chu khopi theng Jerusalem’ah achengun ahi. Chule Judah leh Benjamin khopi dang danga cheng ho chu vangvet na a kon'in som lah a khat bou hichea cheng ding chun alhengdoh un, adang ho se vangchu ama ama chenna mun'a achen sahun ahi.  
\v 2 Ama cham chama Jerusalem'a cheng dinga hung kipedoh ho chu mipiten pachat na apeovin ahi.  
\v 3 Hichea hin gamkai khat a vaihom ho Jerusalem'a cheng dinga hungho chu ahiuve. (Chule mipi atamjo chu thempu ho, Levi te, Hou-In lhacha ho chuleh Solomon lhacha ho sonle pah ho Judah khopi hoa ama in cheha cheng ho ahiuve. \x + \xo 11:3 \xt Nehemiah 7:73\x*  
\v 4 Ahinlah Judah le Benjamin na konna mi phabep khat Jerusalem’a achengun ahi. Chule Judah phunga kon'in: Uzzia chapa Athai’ah, Zechariah chapa, Amariah chapa, Shephatiah chapa, Mahalalel chapa, Perez insung mi ngen ahiuve.)  
\v 5 Baruch chapa Maaseiah, Col-hozah chapa, Hazaiah chapa, Adaiah chapa, Joiarib chapa, Zechariah chapa, Shelah insung mitea kon ahiuve.  
\v 6 Jerusalem'a cheng Perez chilhah mi jali le somgup le get ahiuve; amaho chu abonchauva mithupeh cheh ahiuve.  
\v 7 Benjamin phunga kon'in; Meshullam chapa Sallu, Joed chapa, Pedaiah chapa, Kolaiah chapa, Maaseiah chapa, Ithiel chapa, Jeshaiah chapa ahiuve.  
\v 8 Ama banna hin Gabbai le Sallai abon’un sopi mi jako le somni le get alhingun ahi.  
\v 9 Amaho vaihom lenpen chu Zicri chapa Joel ahin, ama hi khopi sunga vaihom anichanna Hassenuah chapa Judah in akithopi ahi.  
\v 10 Thempuho a kon'in: Joiarib chapa Jedaiah, Jakin;  
\v 11 Chule Hilkiah chapa Seraiah, Meshullam chapa, Zadok chapa, Meraioth chapa, Ahitub chapa, Pathen Hou-In vesuiya pangpa chutoh ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche banna hin Hou-In a natong akithokhom ho chu mi jaget le somni le ni ahiuve. chujongleh Jeroham chapa Adaiah, Pelaliah chapa, Amzi chapa, Zechariah chapa, Pashhur chapa, Malkijah chapa;  
\v 13 Chule atoh khompi ho chu mi ja ni le somli le ni ahiuve, ama hon a insung uva aluboh cheh ahiuve. Hiche ban nahin Azarel chapa Amashsai ahin, Ahzai chapa, Meshillemoth chapa, Immer chapa ahiuve.  
\v 14 Chuleh akithopiu athupi cheh ho chu mi jakhat le somni le get ahiuve. Amaho lah a vaihom lenpen chu Haggedolim chapa Zabdiel ahi.  
\v 15 Levi te akon’in: Hasshub chapa Shemaiah ahin, Azrikam chapa, Hashabiah chapa, Bunni chapa ahiuve.  
\v 16 Hiche bannah Pathen Hou-In polang natong vesuiya pang Shabbethai le Jozabad ahi lhon'e.  
\v 17 Chujongleh Mica chapa Mattaniah, Zabdi chapa, Asaph chilhah ahiuvin thangvah na le taona'a lamkai ahi lhon'e. Hiche bannah Mattaniah akithopia pang Bakbukiah ahin chuleh Shammua chapa Abda, Galal chapa, Jeduthun chapa ahiuve.  
\v 18 Abonchauvin khopi thenga um Levi te chu mi jani le somget le li alhinge.  
\v 19 Kelkot ngah ho a kon'in: Akkub, Talmon, chuleh akilhonpiho chu mi jakhat le somsagi le ni ahiuvin amaho hin kelkot angah’un ahi.  
\v 20 Thempu dang ho le Levi te chuleh Israel dang ho chu a insung’u goulo na dungjuijin Judah khopi ho’ah achengun ahi.  
\v 21 Ziha le Gishpa lamkainan Hou-In lhacha ho chu abonun Ophel lhang chung’ah ana chengun ahi.  
\v 22 Chule Jerusalem a um Levi te vaihom lenpen chu Bani chapa Uzzi ahi; Hashabiah chapa, Mattaniah chapa, Mica chapa, Asaph chilhah ahiuve. Amaho insung hi Pathen Hou-In a lasa a pang ahiuve.  
\v 23 Amaho hin leng thupeh dungjuiya aniseh a amopoh nao hi atohdoh diu ahi.  
\v 24 Meshezabel chapa Pethahiah hi Judah chapa Zerah chilhah ahin mipi kivaipoh na a lengpa thumop a pang ahi.  
\v 25 Polam khoneo neova cheng ho chu ahileh Judah chate phabep jong alouman jouseu pumin Kiriath-arba le akhoneo dung jousea acheng uvin chujongleh Dibon kho leh akhoneo dung jousea jong achengun Jekabzeel le akhoneo dung jousea jong acheng’uvin ahi.  
\v 26 Hiti hin Jeshua jong achenguvin, Moladah a achengun chule Beth-pelet mun'a jong acheng uvin ahi.  
\v 27 Hazarshual a jong achengun, Beersheba khopi le akhoneo dung jousea jong achenguve.  
\v 28 Ziklag khoa jong achengun, Meconah kho le akhoneo dung jousea jong achenguve.  
\v 29 En-rimmon khoa achenguvin, Zorah khoa achenguvin, Jarmuth khoa jong achenguvin ahi.  
\v 30 Zanoah le Adullam kho chule akhoneo dung jousea jong achenguvin, Lachish khopileh aloumun jousea jong chuleh Azekah le akhoneo dung jousea jong achengun ahi. Hiti hin Judah mipite chu Beersheba a kon'in lhanglam Hinnom phaicham geiyin achenglut’uvin ahi.  
\v 31 Benjamin chate jong chu Geba khopia pat akal lam sea ahung cheng pan uvin, Micmash khoa achengun, Aija khoa achenguvin, Bethel khopi leh akhoneo dung jousea jong achenguvin ahi.  
\v 32 Anathoth a jong achengun, Nob khoa achengun, Ananiah khoa jong achenguvin ahi.  
\v 33 Hazor khoa achenguvin, Ramah khoa achenguvin, Gittaim khoa achengun ahi.  
\v 34 Hadid, Zeboim, Nebalat kho hoa achengun ahi.  
\v 35 Lod, Ono chuleh thingthem bol ho phaicham a achenglut un ahi.  
\v 36 Levi te phabep Judah gam'a anacheng ho chu Benjamin phungmi hotoh achen khom sah tauve.   
\c 12  
\s1 Thempu Holeh Levi te Thusim  
\p
\v 1 Hiche ho hi Shealtiel chapa Zerubbabel le thempulen Jeshua toh hung kinungle thempu ho leh Levi te chu ahiuve: Seraiah, Jeremiah, Ezra;  
\v 2 Amariah, Malluch, Hattush;  
\v 3 Shecaniah, Harim, Meremoth;  
\v 4 Iddo, Ginnethon, Abijah;  
\v 5 Miniamin, Moadiah, Bilgah;  
\v 6 Shemaiah, Joiarib, Jedaiah;  
\v 7 Sallu, Amok, Hilkiah chule Jedaiah, amaho hi Jeshua khanga thempu lamkai ho le atohkhom pi hou chu ahiuve.  
\v 8 Levi te amaho toh hung kinungle ho chu Jeshua, Binnui, Kidmiel, Sherebiah, Judah, chuleh Mattaniah ama hi atoh khompi hotoh thangvah na lasah na lamkai ahi.  
\v 9 Atohkhom pi hou Bakbukiah le Unni hin Hou-In sunga kin kibol teng amaho chu toh kimai ngat ton ana ding jiuvin ahi.  
\v 10 Thempulen Jeshua chu Joiakim pa ahi, Joiakim chu Eliashib pa ahi. Eliashib chu Joiada pa ahi.  
\v 11 Joiada chu Johanan pa ahi. Johanan chu Jaddua pa ahi.  
\v 12 Tun Joiakim thempulen ahiphat in insung lamkai ho chu noiya ho hi ahiuve: Meraiah chu Seraiah insung mite lamkai ahin, Hananiah chu Jeremiah insung lamkai ahi.  
\v 13 Meshullam chu Ezra insung lamkai ahi. Jehohanan chu Amariah insung lamkai ahi.  
\v 14 Jonathan chu Malluch insung lamkai ahi. Joseph chu Shecaniah insung lamkai ahi.  
\v 15 Adna chu Harim insung lamkai ahi. Helkai chu Meremoth insung lamkai ahi.  
\v 16 Zechariah chu Iddo insung lamkai ahi. Meshullam chu Ginnethon insung lamkai ahi.  
\v 17 Zichri chu Abijah insung lamkai ahi. Miniamin'insung lamkai jong ana um'in ahi. Piltai chu Moadiah insung lamkai anahi.  
\v 18 Shammua chu Bilgah insung lamkai anahi. Jahonathan chu Shemaiah insung lamkai anahi.  
\v 19 Mettenai chu Joiarib insung lamkai anahi. Uzzi chu Jedaiah insung lamkai anahi.  
\v 20 Kallai chu Sallu insung lamkai anahi. Eber chu Amok insung lamkai anahi.  
\v 21 Hashabiah chu Hilkiah insung lamkai anahi. Nathanel chu Jedaiah insung lamkai anahi.  
\v 22 Eliashib, Joiada, Jonathan, chule Jaddua chu thempulen anahi nao kumsung chun Levi te insung minbu chu phatah in ana kikoiyin ahi.  
\v 23 Levi te insung lamkai ho minbu chu khanggui thusimbu a ana kikoijin hichu Eliashib tupa Johanan khang geiya umsuh peh a ahi.  
\v 24 Hicheng hi Levi te lamkai ho insung mite ahiuve: Hashabiah, Sherebiah, Jeshua, Binnui, Kadmiel, chule akiloi khompi ho ahiuvin, amaho hi thangvah na le kipa thusei na kin kibol teng kingatto jia ahiuvin Pathen mipa David in ana thupeh banga loikhat chu loikhat toh kidonbut toji ahiuve.  
\v 25 Hichea chun Mattaniah Bakbukiah chuleh Obadiah jong ana panguve. Meshullam, Talmon, chule Akkub chu kelkot phunga thilkeo koina indan chu angahtup ma panga ahiuve.  
\v 26 Amaho hin Jehozadok chapa Jeshua chapa Joiakim chule gamvaipo Nehemiah leh thempulen danthu them Ezra khanglaiya ana toh’u ahi.   
\s1 Jerusalem Kulpi Kithenso  
\p
\v 27 Jerusalem kulpi bang athah chu thensona kin na hi ahung kithopina diuvin gamsung muntin na um Levi te chu akoukhom uvin ahi. Amaho chun atumgingu thih pheng kisai gin, selangdah ginleh semjang kisaiging puma hiche kin loupia hi thangvah na lasah puma thanomtah a pan alah u ahi.  
\v 28 Jerusalem vel'a Netophath mite khohoa konna lasa ho akhom sohkeiyun ahi.  
\v 29 Beth-gilgal leh thinglhang gam Geba leh Azmaveth kom veldunga kon'in jong ahungun ahi. Ajeh chu lasa miho hin Jerusalem veldunga chu chenmun ana kisem u ahi.  
\v 30 Thempu ho leh Levi te chu amasan amaho leh amaho akisutheng un chujouvin mipi ho leh kelkot ho chule kulpi bang chu asuthengun ahi.  
\v 31 Keiman Juda lamkai ho chu kulpi bang chunga chun kapuijin thangvah na pe dingin lathem hon ni kaga gong toh'in ahi. Lathem honkhat chu Eh-Kelkot lang ajonun, lathem honkhat chun lhanglam ajonun Eh-Kelkot lang kulpi bang chung langa chun aheuvin ahi.  
\v 32 Hoshiah leh Judah lamkai akehkhat in ajuijun ahi.  
\v 33 Azariah, Ezra, Meshullam;  
\v 34 Judah, Benjamin, Shemaiah, chuleh Jeremiah jong ahiuve.  
\v 35 Hicheng jou chun sumkon mut thempu ho phabep ahungun Jonathan chapa Zachariah, Shemaiah chapa, Mettaniah chapa, Mecaiah chapa, Zaccur chapa, Asaph chilhah ho jonghi apanguve.  
\v 36 Chuleh Zechariah tohkhompi ho chu Shemaiah, Azarel, Milalai, Gilalai, Maai, Nethanel, Judah chuleh Hanani ahiuve. Chule amaho hin Pathen mipa David in anasuh tohsa tumging thei ho chu ana mang hauvin ahi. Ezra in mipi kijot ho chu ana lamkaiyin ahi.  
\v 37 Twikhuh kelkot na kon chun khopi kulpi banga kal touna kalbia chun jangpet in acheuvin David khopi lang ajonun ahi. Ama hon David inchu aho paovin chuin solang Twi Kelkot lang chu ajon’un ahi.  
\v 38 Lathem hon ni na ho chun thangvah pumin sahlang ajonun lang khat lam a chun avel’un amahotoh kimuto dingin acheuvin ahi. Kenjong amaho nung kajuiyin mipi akehkhat chutoh kalhonne, kulpi bang vumma kacheuvin meikhulong hung kitundoh chungvum langa kacheuvin, kulpi bang ningkoi lang geiyin kacheuve.  
\v 39 Chuin Ephraim kelkot chunglam a kacheuvin, kelkot luilang Nga Kelkot kom Hananel insung lam, Kelngoi hong Kelkot phung geiyin kacheuvin ahi, chujouvin miho chu kelkot ngah ho din munna chun ahung ding uvin ahi.  
\v 40 Lathem hon ni ho chun thangvah na la sa pumin Pathen Hou-In lang chu ajon’un hilaiya chun apansa tauve. Keileh kaki lhonpi lamkai ho jong hilaiya chun kaum tauve.  
\v 41 Keiho chu sumkon mut thempu ho Eliakim, Maaseiah, Miniamin, Micaiah, Elioenai, Zechariah chuleh Hananiah;  
\v 42 Chule lasaho- Maaseiah, Shemaiah, Eleazer, Uzzi, Jehohanan, Malkijah, Elam chuleh Ezer, mi hicheng hitoh kaki lhonun ahi. Ama hon lathem lamkaipa Jezrahiah mapuina in tum ging toh thon hasah in asauvin ahi.  
\v 43 Hiche kipa thanop ni chun pumgo thilto tamtah anatoh doh’un ahi, ajeh chu Pathen'in mipi chu kipana lentah anapen ahi. Hiche golnop nikhoa hin numei le chapang ho jong ana pangun chule Jerusalem mipite kipana ogin chu gamla tah a kon'in jong akijan ahi.   
\s1 Hou-In’a Pathen Hou Nadia Thilto  
\p
\v 44 Hiche nikho chun maicham ma hung kitoh doh ho, lhosohga masa hung kitoh ho leh hopsom hung kitohdoh ho kholna indan ho vesui dingin mi phabep akipansah in ahi. Danthun angeh dungjuiya thempu ho leh Levi te chan ding dol khopi pamlanga chengho kom'a hindong dingin amaho chun mopohna aneiyun ahi. Ajeh chu Judah mipite hin thempu ho leh Levi te natoh na a hin alunglhai lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 45 ama hon David leh achapa Solomon ana thupeh bangin Pathen kin leh kisuh thengna kin hi atongun ahi, chuleh lasa a pang ho leh kelkot ngah hon jong ajongun ahi. \x + \xo 12:45 \xt 1 Thusimbu 25:1-8; \xt 1 Thusimbu 26:12\x*  
\v 46 Vahchoi la le Pathen thangvah na lasah na a lathem ho lamkai ding tohgon chu David le Asaph nikho lai peh a patna hung che jom peh ahi.  
\v 47 Hiti chun Zerubbabel le Nehemiah khang hin Israel mipiten lasa ho leh kelkot ngah ho chule Levi te neh le chah ding niseh in ahin pohpeh jiuvin ahi. Levi te chun amahoa thilmua kon chun Aaron chilhah thempuho ding phabep ape jiuvin ahi.   
\c 13  
\s1 Nehemiah In Thil Dang Dang Asemphat  
\p
\v 1 Hiche nikho ma ma hin Mose lekhabu chu mipi ho lah a asimdoh un ahileh Ammon miho leh Moab miho chu Pathen houkhom na a lutthei lou diu ahi ti amudoh’un ahi. \x + \xo 13:1 \xt Danbu Ni Na 23:3-5\x*  
\v 2 Ajeh chu ama hon gamthip noiya chun Israel te an le twi anape nom pouvin ahi. Chusangin ama hon Balaam chu apa-lah a sapset sah ding ana gouvin ahi, ahin Pathen'in hiche sapset na chu phattheiboh na in ana lehei peh in ahi. \x + \xo 13:2 \xt Minbu 22:1-6\x*  
\v 3 Hiche danthu kijihna laitah chu akiphah poh tengleh gamchom miho chu apet petna houkhom na a kon chun anodoh jiuvin ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche masanghin i-Pathen’u Hou-In’a thilkeo koina indan ho vesui dinga kinganse Eliashib hi Tobiah inko ana hikhan;  
\v 5 Ama hin thilkoina indan lentah khat chu Tobiah khut nah ana pedoh khan ahi. Hiche indan chu tumasang’a Hou-In thil ho leh chang hopsom lengpitwi thah, Olive thao chuleh thempu ho ding maicham koina kinei anahi (hiche ho hi Levi te le, lasa miho, chuleh kelkot ngah hoa dinga ana kigong chu anahi.)  
\v 6 Hiche pet hin keima Jerusalem a kana um'in ahi, ajeh chu Babylon lengpa Artaxerxes vaihom kum somthum le kum ni channa a chu akom'a kana kile kit na dingin phalna kahin kilah in ahi.  
\v 7 Jerusalem kahung nung lhun jouvin Eliashib min Pathen Hou-In indan sung khat ana pehdoh jenga hitobanga thil dihlou anabol khah chu kahedoh tan ahi.  
\v 8 Hichu keiman nom mo kasa behseh jeng tan Tobiah thilkeo ho jouse chu indan sunga kon chun kale mangpeh tan ahi.  
\v 9 Hijouchun indan sung ho chu kasuhtheng sah in, Pathen Hou-In thilkeo ho leh, chang hopsom ho chuleh gimnamtui ho chu kale lhohlut kittai.  
\v 10 Chuleh keiman Levi te chan ding anneh kigong sa ho chu ana peh louvu kamudoh tan, hijeha chu Pathen houkhom na a analamkai ding ho chu ama loulang cheh a natong dingin ana kinungle tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 13:10 \xt Danbu Ni Na 12:19\x*  
\v 11 Keiman gangtah in lamkai ho chu kakimaito pin kasei tan ahi; “Ipi dinga Pathen Hou-In hi nahsah moa kikoija hitam?” kati. Hiche jouchun Levi te chu kavel koudoh in atohdiu kincheh u chu katohsah kit tan ahi.  
\v 12 Hiti chun Judah mipite ho chun achang hopsom hou, lengpitwi thahho chule Olive thaoho chu Hou-In thil koina hoa ahin pelut kit tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 13:12 \xt Malachi 3:10\x*  
\v 13 Keiman thil koina in na vaihom ho: Shelemiah thempupa, Zadok danthu thempa, chule Pedaiah kiti Levi mikhat chu atohnao muncheh a kakoi kitin ahi. Chuleh Mattaniah tupa Zaccur chapa Hanan chu akithopi diuvin kakiojin ahi. Amaho hi seiphat chang cheh ahiuvin hiti chun ama hon a Levi chan khompi hou chu kitah tah in achandiu achansah soh un ahi.  
\v 14 Vo ka Pathen katoh phat nau ho hi geldoh inlang ka Pathen Hou-In ding leh akin kitohna hoa kitah tah a katoh hi neisuhmil peh hihbeh in.  
\v 15 Hiche nikho laihin, Judah mihon cholngah nikhoa lengpiga achil’u kamun ahi. Ama hon hange mim ahin pouvin sangan chunga akhangdoh un, alengpitwi’ule lengpiga theichang ho leh thilsoh jouse Jerusalem’ah ahin pouvin cholngah nia joh dingin ahin pouvin ahi. Hijeh chun hiche khoa atohga soh’u ajoh jeh un kaphoh in ahi. \x + \xo 13:15 \xt Potdohbu 20:8-10; Danbu Ni Na 5:12-14; Jeremiah 17:21,22\x*  
\v 16 Jerusalem a cheng hon Tyre gam a kon'in nga ahin, kiveina thil jatchom chom ho ahin polut’un ahi. Amaho hin Jerusalem a Judah mite lah a cholngah nikhon ajoh’un ahi!  
\v 17 Hijeh chun keiman Judah lamkaite chu kaki maitopin hitin kasei tan ahi; “Ipi dinga nang hon hitobang tah a hi thilse nabol’uva cholngah nikho hi nasuh boh u hitam?”  
\v 18 “Ipu ipa teuvin hitobanga hi na anatoh jiu jeh a, Pathen'in eiho chungle ikhopiuva hi hahsatna ana chuhsah ji hilou ham? Tuhin nang hon hitobang tah hin cholngah nikho nasuboh un Israel chunga Pathen lunghan na khoh cheh nahin polut tauve.  
\v 19 Hichun keiman cholngah ni masang nilhah kho hungjin phatleh Jerusalem kelkot chu kha jeng ding cholngah ni kichai tokah a honlou dingin thu kapen ahi. Cholngah nia kiveina thilho hung kipoh lut louna dingin keiman lhacha ho phabep chu kelkot kangasah in ahi.  
\v 20 Kivei miho le thil jat chom chom joh ho chu Jerusalem khopam’ah khat vei nivei ageh khovah un ahi.  
\v 21 Amaho chu kahousen, “Nanghon hiche kulpi bang vella hi ibola geh khovah nahiovem? Hitia hi naum kit’ule kamat diu ahi!” kati. Hiti chun amaho cholngah ni ahung kit tapouve.  
\v 22 Hijouchun keiman Levi te chu amaho leh amaho kisutheng ding leh cholngah ni athenga umsah jing nadinga kelkot ngah dingin thu kapen ahi. O ka Pathen hiche katoh phat nahi geldoh in! Na mingailutna longlou kidangtah jallin kachunga na hepina kaiyin.  
\v 23 Hiche phatlai tah chun keiman Judah mi phabep min Ashdod Ammon leh Moab numei ho akichen piuve ti kahin hedoh tan ahi. \x + \xo 13:23 \xt Potdohbu 34:11-16; Danbu Ni Na 7:1-5\x*  
\v 24 Hiche banna chun, achateu akeh khat in Ashdod paole paodang athouvin, Judah pao atho theipouvin ahi.  
\v 25 Hijeh chun amaho chu kakimaito pin kasam sen ahi. Mi phabep chu kavon chuleh asammu kabolhah pehin ahi. Keiman amaho chu achateu hiche gam'a cheng hou neilou ho toh achateu akichensah louna diuvin Pathen min panin kakihahsel sah in ahi.  
\v 26 Hiche jeh a hi Israel leng Solomon achonset lochu? Keiman kaseijin; “Namdang leng ama toh tekah pithei aumpoi, ama chu Pathen'in angailun Israel te jouse leng ahisah in ahi. Ahiyeng vang'in gamdang mi ajiten achonset sah in ahi.” \x + \xo 13:26 \xt 2 Samuel 12:24,25; \xt 1 Lgt 11:1-8\x*   
\p
\v 27 Iti dan a nang hon gamchom a numei ho nakichen piuva Pathen mitmua kitah loutah a na um’uva hitobang tah a chonsetna hi natoh dohu hitam?   
\p
\v 28 Thempulen Eliashab chapa Joiada chate lah a khat’in Horon mi Sanballat chanu ana kichenpi jeh in kakom'a kon'in kakai dohtan ahi. \x + \xo 13:28 \xt Nehemiah 4:1\x*  
\v 29 O ka Pathen amaho hi geldoh in, ajeh chu ama hon thempu ho leh Levi te gimneitah a akitepnau asuboh tauve.  
\v 30 Hiti chun keiman gamchom mi toh kitimat na jouse chu kasuthengin thempu ho leh Levi te chu akin cheh’u pochil tah a atohna diuvin natoh kagon toh peh cheh in ahi.  
\v 31 Chuleh keiman maicham a ding thing aning lhinga ahin peh na diu leh lhosoh masa apha cha cha ahin pohlutna diuvin kagongtoh in ahi. O ka Pathen, hiche hi keima neikhohsah na in hin gel doh teiyin.   